args:
The prince protects someone who is about to
be attacked by Ayaha and Otoha, but in so
doing reveals his location to the mob.
The party is surrounded and about to be
attacked when a shot rings out and Prince
Leonidas appears before the group.
There's no point in fighting further!\nJust get out of here already!
He's a cheeky one, isn't he, Aya?
He certainly is, Oto.\nBut the real fun starts now.
Dammit! Where the hell are you, Other?!
▷Look! Someone is coming!◁\nWe must make a tactical retreat.
Ooo, a new puppet! Okay then, we'll start\nthe ripping-apart with that one.
Shut up already! We don't take orders!
What the devil?! Are you people pawns\nof the Other?! S-stop! Nooooo!
I will never let you harm my people!
Tch! Boring. I thought we had more\npuppets to play with.
Aya, let's go back. This is stupid\nand I'm tired of it.
Let's do that, Oto. The ＂festival＂ was\nmore boring than I expected.
Yeah, it's not deep. More importantly,\nare YOU all right?
He's here! The Other is here!
Hey, look! He's right there! Get him!
Son of a sandwich, they found us...\nLet's go, boss! We're runnin' the other\ndirection!
Dammit, they're coming that way, too!\nWe're gonna end up surrounded!
We're at a dead end; I have no choice\nbut to try and reason with them.
Watch yourself, everyone! Ain't no telling\nwhat evil the Other's gonna get up to!
Let's take him out before he starts\nusing all his strange magic!
Everyone, stop! I'm not the Other!
You damn liar! If you aren't the Other,\nthen where'd he disappear to?!
The Other was absorbed and destroyed\nbefore we could fight him!
It's true! You have to believe us!
Then how do you explain the black dragon\nthat showed up and started wrecking the\ncapital after you all left, huh?
Black dragon... Wait, are you saying\nthat a void dragon has appeared?!
I lost my fields and my home, but there\nare others who lost parents or children!
Don't play us for fools! You're controlling\nthe dragon and trying to rule Alberia!
Okay, how in the world did you people\ncome to THAT conclusion?!
It's obviously him controlling the dragon;\nhe's the one with the Other's power\nand the dragon's blood!
I would never do something like that!\nI'm trying to create a world where\neveryone can live in PEACE!
Don't you people realize how hard my\ndarling has worked for all of you?!
Enough lies! We're gonna take you down\nand reclaim our old lives!
Take him out! Destroy the Other!
This ain't good, boss. We may not have\na choice but to fight these folks.
I can't hurt them, and yet...
They're all coming this way, Brother!\nYou must protect yourself!
